    "question_id" : 1565388,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>It is possible to increase heap size allocated by the JVM in eclipse directly \nIn eclipse IDE goto</p>\n\n<p>Run---->Run Configurations---->Arguments</p>\n\n<p>Enter -Xmx1g(It is used to set the max size like Xmx256m or Xmx1g...... m-->mb g--->gb)</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3037706,
      "reputation" : 131,
      "user_id" : 2575388,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/cc07206f9659e11a170546dcc342b9a4?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
